A re-implementation of libpiano (from http://github.com/PromyLOPh/pianobar) in PHP.
Idea to re-implement in my language of choice is courtesy of pithos (http://kevinmehall.net/p/pithos/)

PHP class to facilitate interactions with the Pandora streaming Internet radio service.
So far, very basic functionality
 * Login
 * Retrieve station list

Cheers!
